    "title": "Immediate Requirement Production Engineer at Nestle India",
    "description": "Nestle India has an exciting opening for a Production Engineer at our Jabalpur office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Nestle India:\nNestle India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nestle India!",
